39365>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
39366>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
39367>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
39368>>>            WebSet pbRender of oNewDetail to True
39369>>>            WebSet pbVisible of oBtnJugadorPosicion to True
39370>>>        End
